{"tid":2512742,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國最遠的核電廠都比福島近","createTime":"2021-05-02T03:46:03.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-02T04:25:38.000Z","uid":261647,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"2511a6add75d81a03b9c441debca3b3f964a4475","tid":2512742,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T03:46:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/grant0516/posts/4505570092793681\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgrant0516%2Fposts%2F4505570092793681&d=Z1ElB6oaYTZYlgUQOIdQNrnp9gp%2BSvHPFRLSSJzTNPo%3D&h=7752aecd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/grant0516/posts/4505570092793681</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQU8pTpFgcDqgYY9VFohK3tiG76hkBX3GXJZC3FcdqKkw?filename=XyvGJiH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXyvGJiH.jpg&h=cba946a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n作者：曾韋禎<br />\n<br />\n中國最遠的核電廠都比福島近<br />\n<br />\n台灣的紅色政治、媒體勢力，最近狂帶仇日民粹的風向。不過事實上，所有核電廠都會排放核廢水，而技術落後的中國，核廢水比處理過的福島廢水更毒；且中國核電廠離台灣更近，最遠的還只有福島的一半距離。"},{"pid":"98dc52ca7d5ab27512a8a9ea20be81e726403a2b","tid":2512742,"uid":159448,"like":3,"dislike":7,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T03:50:53.000Z","msg":"問題你不嬲都唔會食中國魚生 但係會食日本魚生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d88eb8b43b7cb180d1a3eb4d8f5220ac694f6e1","tid":2512742,"uid":198225,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"98dc52ca7d5ab27512a8a9ea20be81e726403a2b","tid":2512742,"uid":159448,"like":3,"dislike":7,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T03:50:53.000Z","msg":"問題你不嬲都唔會食中國魚生 但係會食日本魚生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T04:00:38.000Z","msg":"煮熟就冇毒？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  真係有毒，住起個到o既日本人會首先出聲，中國就唔知了。"},{"pid":"a176fb13c99cbf833a79968da21cb0ad2d66e5d9","tid":2512742,"uid":257491,"like":2,"dislike":9,"score":-7,"quote":{"